prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析睪固酮檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL: Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL, preservative.
R1 Anti-testosterone-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL: Biotinylated monoclonal anti-testosterone antibody (mouse) 55 ng/mL; phosphate buffer 40 mmol/L, pH 7.0; preservative.
R2 Testosterone-peptide~Ru(bpy)2+3 (black cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL: Testosterone derivative, labeled with ruthenium complex 3 ng/mL; releasing reagent ANS/Norgestrel; phosphate buffer 40 mmol/L, pH 7.0; preservative.

CalSet - working solutions
•	TESTO Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
•	TESTO Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
Testosterone (from plant material) in two concentration range (approx. <3.5 nmol/L or <1.0 ng/mL and approx. 45 nmol/L or 13 ng/mL) in a human serum matrix.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 在體外利用電化學發光免疫分析法(Electrochemiluminescence immunoassay“ECLIA”)在Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上定量檢測人類血清和血漿中的睪固酮。
